{
  "stem": "20035.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had no idea if he's going to do it, yes or not.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Although, the same time, I have to tell you a little anecdote.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because maybe you-- during that time, my brother met a gentleman who was an uncle of a friend of his classmate, naturally, a Jewish gentleman, who recognized my brother.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the second-- the first morning, after the first night which was miserable and we were naturally very hungry, especially kids, suddenly he said that he has some food for us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these gentlemen opened up the briefcase and from the briefcase they took out raw eggs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I looked at him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My brother looked at him now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Great, you have raw eggs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because he told us be careful, they are raw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he got a little pocket knife from his pocket-- he was an engineer-- and opened up-- made a little hole on one end of the egg, then made a hole, put his finger and he turn it over, made an egg and the other hole.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Just told me I was the first one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He said, put your finger on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He said, put it to your mouth and suck out the egg.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I looked at him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was a finicky eater, difficult eater.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I said, no way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that's what I still feel today.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That my brother slapped me across the face.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he said, from now on, whatever they give you to eat, if you want to survive, you eat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I sucked that egg out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Till today, don't show me sunny-sides up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From there-- from the Budapest police quarters, we were taken after-- well, I think it was the third day-- by truck to a internment camp-- camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
